{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your family is in danger, and you've been pulled into a deadly game to save them. Carefully analyze every criminal who gets into your car, understand their traits, and survive with the right strategies without making them angry.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Observe</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dangerous Passengers</strong>: Killers, thieves, fraudsters... Each has different personalities and danger levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Psychological Analysis:</strong> Determine the criminal type from the behavior of your passengers and complete the journey without making them angry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/observe.gif?t=1729269407\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the applications on your computer to access the information you need or forcefully retrieve it from the deep web. You might find information in the deep web on how to defuse a bomb placed under your car. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/terminal.gif?t=1729269407\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Survive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Complete Missions:</strong> Use the notes in your logbook to transport your passenger without angering them and if you survive, send your notes to BK26.<br><strong>Wrong Place, Wrong Time:</strong> There\u2019s no guarantee you\u2019ll survive, inside or outside your car. You should be alert at all times.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/death.gif?t=1729269407\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Determine Your Fate</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Is there anyone to help? Complete BK26\u2019s missions or find different ways to determine your fate. Not for yourself, but for your family.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai